Overview
This project implements a Movie Recommendation System using the MovieLens dataset. It combines data preprocessing, model training, evaluation, and visualization to generate personalized movie suggestions for users.

Features
ğŸ“‚ Data Loading: Import movies, ratings, tags, and links from MovieLens dataset.

