ğŸ”€ Train/Test Split: Divide dataset into training and testing sets.

ğŸ¤– Model Training: Train multiple regression models (Linear Regression, Decision Tree, KNN).

ğŸ“Š Evaluation: Compare models using RMSE and RÂ² metrics.

ğŸ¯ Best Model Selection: Use the best-performing model for predictions.

ğŸ¬ Personalized Recommendations: Generate top movie suggestions for a given user.

ğŸ·ï¸ User Tags Integration: Display user-provided tags for recommended movies.

ğŸŒ External Links: Include IMDb and TMDb identifiers for recommended movies.

